# AYALUZ DESIGN SYSTEM

## Brand Essence
AyaLuz is a luxury spiritual retreat platform focused on ayahuasca healing journeys, sacred ceremonies, emotional transformation, and conscious wellness experiences in Peru.

The visual identity should feel:
- sacred
- cinematic
- grounded
- elegant
- healing
- premium
- organic
- timeless

Avoid:
- startup/SaaS aesthetics
- corporate UI
- neon gradients
- overly modern tech feeling
- excessive glassmorphism
- cluttered layouts

