# Hero Sections

Hero sections should:
- use cinematic nature imagery
- contain emotional spiritual copy
- include dark image overlays
- use left-aligned editorial layouts
- avoid centered SaaS structures

---

# Cards

Cards should:
- use soft transparency
- have subtle borders
- rounded corners
- calm shadows
- warm backgrounds

---

# Cards drop shadow
attributes:
- X=0
- Y=12
- Blur=40
- Spread=0
- color= #141916
- opacity= 20%
---

# Animations

Animations should be:
- subtle
- slow
- calm
- premium
- non-distracting

Avoid:
- excessive motion
- bouncing effects
- flashy transitions

---

# Technical Stack

- Next.js App Router
- TailwindCSS
- TypeScript
- Sanity CMS
- Vercel deployment

---

# Rules For AI Generation

Whenever generating new UI:
- maintain AyaLuz visual language
- preserve typography consistency
- preserve spacing consistency
- preserve color harmony
- avoid introducing new visual systems

All future sections must feel part of the same sacred luxury retreat ecosystem.